<PB N="44" REF="53">
that we are duft</HI><NOTE N="&ast;" PLACE="foot">P&s;al. ix. 8.&mdash;cii. 17.&mdash;cxlvi. 7.&mdash;lxviii. 5.&mdash;cxlvii. 3. ciii. 14.&mdash;&amp;$c.</NOTE>.&mdash;If the
